text: Ærest on ða ea, andlang dice on hocces clif.
Of hocces clif on snelles pytt.
Of snelles pytt, andlang dic, on cealfa hlinc.
Of cealfa hlinc on hafakes beorh.
Of hafakes beorh on ðone stan beorh.
Of ðan stan beorhge on ræst hlinc.
Of deopan delle on ðone readan stan.
Of ðan readan stane on wærmundes stan.
Of wærmundes stane on langan hlinc.
Of langan hlince on ðone holan weg.
Of holan wege on kyneware treowe.
Of kyneware treowe on grenan hlince in to ðan fleote æt ho, of ðan fleote þæt eft in ða ea.
